{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":549408,"duration_api_ms":486738,"num_turns":118,"result":"The fix is complete. Let me provide a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Summary\n\nThe issue was Python 3.12 compatibility in DVC 0.89.0. In Python 3.12, the internal `pathlib` API changed significantly:\n\n1. **`_from_parts`** method was removed from `pathlib.PurePath` and `pathlib.Path`\n2. **`_cparts`** attribute was renamed to **`_tail`**\n3. **`_flavour.is_supported`** attribute was removed (flavour is now just the path module itself)\n\n### Changes Made\n\n**`dvc/path_info.py`** (2 fixes):\n1. `PathInfo.__new__`: Changed `cls._from_parts(args)` → `pathlib.PurePath.__new__(cls, *args)` to fix the constructor for Python 3.12's new internal structure\n2. `PathInfo.isin`: Changed `_cparts` → `_tail` to use the renamed attribute\n\n**`tests/dir_helpers.py`** (1 fix, required for tests to run):\n- `TmpDir.__new__`: Replaced the removed `_from_parts(args, init=False)` + `_init()` pattern with the Python 3.12-compatible `object.__new__(cls)` + `_raw_paths` + `_load_parts()` approach\n\n### Results\n\n- All 17 `test_path_info.py` tests: **PASS** ✓\n- All `test_cache.py` tests (13): **PASS** ✓\n- All `test_gc.py` tests (12): **PASS** ✓\n- All `test_rwlock.py` tests (4): **PASS** ✓\n- 258/258 unit tests: **PASS** ✓\n- 2 tests in `test_version.py` fail due to a pre-existing test regex bug (`\\d\\.\\d\\.\\d` doesn't match `3.12.3`), not related to the source code changes","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"e5cb6012-d1e3-459c-9ed8-50b215f267b5","total_cost_usd":11.301850499999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":3588306,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1016,"cache_read_input_tokens":472425,"output_tokens":26093,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"cache_deleted_input_tokens":0,"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed":{"inputTokens":3588306,"outputTokens":26093,"cacheReadInputTokens":472425,"cacheCreationInputTokens":1016,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":11.301850499999999,"contextWindow":196000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"1549a7f6-0c3c-4d8d-9fc3-e2157afb76f0"}
